### BILH Smoke Test API Calls
### Use with REST Client extension or similar HTTP client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@systemSlug = bilh

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Chat API
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "systemSlug": "{{systemSlug}}",
  "question": "What can you tell me about Beth Israel Lahey Health from the ingested data?"
}

### Meeting Prep API
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meeting-prep
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "systemSlug": "{{systemSlug}}",
  "meetingType": "discovery",
  "audienceDescription": "CIO and VP Applications",
  "myObjective": "Understand their cloud and EHR roadmap",
  "timeBoxMinutes": 60
}

### Strategy Briefing API
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/strategy-briefing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "systemSlug": "{{systemSlug}}",
  "horizonMonths": 12
}

### Daily Briefing API
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-briefing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "{{systemSlug}}"
}

### Account Plan GET
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/account-plan?systemSlug={{systemSlug}}

### Run Pipeline
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/systems/{{systemSlug}}/run-pipeline

